#. Max bytes: 263
msgctxt "Offset_0x132F8_Len_263"
msgid "You can now drink with Akiyoshi-san!\n\nAs you become closer to the customers, your rank within\nthe bar will increase. As your rank increases, you'll\nbe able to drink with more people.\n\nBe assertive about approaching people, or form a bond\nthrough karaoke or darts."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 260
msgctxt "Offset_0x13408_Len_260"
msgid "< 已和秋吉先生成為酒友！ >\n\n只要和客人們培養感情，就能提昇在小酒館中的地位。\n隨著地位提昇，可以和更多人成為酒友。\n\n積極和其他客人攀談，或利用卡拉OK和飛鏢引起注目來提昇友好度吧。"
msgstr ""

